metadata.name: EMERGENCE
metadata.description:
Oil painting on Canvas.


It's time for the world to know you! 
It's time to come out from the deep!
it's time to let your light attract people to you!
my dear son! it's time to show forth what you're made of! 
Go forth! You've endured well!

This is a tale of the boy who came out of all ordeals. The tale of the commoner who became King!
